<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="556" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1437,541,820]" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,541,567]" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">Remarks.</emphasis>
Kojima and van Achterberg (1997) recorded a single female specimen of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1852" box="[1106,1245,542,568]" class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" genus="Epipona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="556" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="variegata">
<emphasis box="[1106,1123,542,567]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">R</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1138,1245,542,567]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">variegata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as “ 
<collectingRegion box="[1294,1402,541,567]" country="Indonesia" name="Sulawesi Utara" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">Sulawesi</collectingRegion>
: nr Luwuk, Bunga, c. 
<quantity box="[357,432,577,604]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="15" pageNumber="556" unit="m" value="300.0">300 m</quantity>
: 1, MT–17, 
<date box="[567,717,577,603]" pageId="15" pageNumber="556" value="1989-11-01" valueMax="1989-11-14" valueMin="1989-11-01">1–14.xi.1989</date>
, C. v. Achterberg (RMNH)”. This is the only 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1852" box="[1225,1362,578,603]" class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" genus="Epipona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="556" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="variegata">
<emphasis box="[1225,1362,578,603]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">R. variegata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
specimen from 
<collectingRegion box="[266,367,613,639]" country="Indonesia" name="Sulawesi Utara" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">Sulawesi</collectingRegion>
I. and we have not found any other specimens of this species among many 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Guerin-Meneville" authorityYear="1831" box="[1203,1313,613,639]" class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" genus="Ropalidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="556" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1203,1313,613,639]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">Ropalidia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
specimens collected in 
<collectingRegion box="[289,390,649,675]" country="Indonesia" name="Sulawesi Utara" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">Sulawesi</collectingRegion>
I. and deposited in MZB and IUNH. The current occurrence/establishment of this species in 
<collectingRegion box="[151,252,685,711]" country="Indonesia" name="Sulawesi Utara" pageId="15" pageNumber="556">Sulawesi</collectingRegion>
I. would need confirmation based on further intensive field research.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
